---
---

<section id="programma" class="section">
  <div class="container">

    <div class="header animate-on-scroll">
      <div class="icon-wrap">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M9 18V5l12-2v13"></path>
          <circle cx="6" cy="18" r="3"></circle>
          <circle cx="18" cy="16" r="3"></circle>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h2>Floorprogramma 2026</h2>
      <p>
        Het programma van Floor Schermerhorn is gevuld met muziek, entertainment en activiteiten voor het hele gezin. Van live bands tot DJ's, van kinderkermis tot markt, alles is voorzien. Het programma wordt nog aangevuld. Houd deze pagina in de gaten!
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="cards animate-on-scroll">
      <article class="program-card">
        <h3>
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"></rect>
            <line x1="16" y1="2" x2="16" y2="6"></line>
            <line x1="8" y1="2" x2="8" y2="6"></line>
            <line x1="3" y1="10" x2="21" y2="10"></line>
          </svg>
          Vrijdag 12 september
        </h3>
        <p>Opening om 19:00 uur met live muziek en entertainment.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="program-card">
        <h3>
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"></rect>
            <line x1="16" y1="2" x2="16" y2="6"></line>
            <line x1="8" y1="2" x2="8" y2="6"></line>
            <line x1="3" y1="10" x2="21" y2="10"></line>
          </svg>
          Zaterdag 13 september
        </h3>
        <p>Volledige dag met markt, truckershow, kinderkermis en live muziek.</p>
      </article>
    </div>

    <p class="notice animate-on-scroll">
      Het programma is nog niet compleet en zal binnenkort worden aangevuld met meer informatie.
    </p>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .section {
    padding-block: var(--space-section);
    background-color: var(--clr-fg);
    color: var(--clr-bg);
  }

  .header {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 48rem;
    margin-inline: auto;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .icon-wrap {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 5rem;
    height: 5rem;
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--clr-primary) 20%, transparent);
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    color: var(--clr-primary);
  }

  h2 {
    color: #fff;
  }

  .header p {
    font-size: var(--fs-lg);
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
    margin-inline: auto;
  }

  .cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
    max-width: 62rem;
    margin-inline: auto;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .cards {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }
  }

  .program-card {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    padding: 2rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .program-card h3 {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--clr-primary);
    font-size: var(--fs-xl);
  }

  .program-card p {
    font-size: var(--fs-lg);
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
    line-height: 1.6;
    max-width: none;
  }

  .notice {
    text-align: center;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
    font-style: italic;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-inline: auto;
    max-width: none;
  }
</style>
